<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">I was looking for some information on soloing at level 31.  I know, an enchanter should never solo but I do enjoy it.  That said, one idea I had was the Ancient Crock spawn in Upper Guk.  That is a fairly safe spawn I think.  I could charm the crocks and not worry about anything else agroing on me.  <br>
Any other ideas where there is a 2 spawn about lv 30 or 31 that an enchanter with a charisma of 200 could kick some but?<hr>Siorn Racharm<br>
