<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Baobob and Chanda Miller in qeynos hills. They are lvl 25 and are by the Surefall Glade zone. You can charm fight them to 34, then head to kunark.<p>

also: Monk in the zone named Konem Matse... can kick the crap outta both millers, and you can take Guard Bixby and Philbin with him, just make sure you have Sow in case charm breaks.<p>

Tiya Xen'Taro<br>
